 "": "Project-Id-Version: eXe 1.04\nReport-Msgid-Bugs-To: \nPOT-Creation-Date: 2013-04-22 16:43+0200\nPO-Revision-Date: 2013-03-07 21:05+0100\nLast-Translator: Andrea Primiani <primiani@dag.it>\nLanguage-Team: Italian <primiani@dag.it>\nPlural-Forms: nplurals=2; plural=(n != 1)\nMIME-Version: 1.0\nContent-Type: text\/plain; charset=utf-8\nContent-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\nGenerated-By: Babel 0.9.6\n", 
 "Checking this option, the exported SCORM file will be editable with eXeLearning.": "Con questa opzione, il file SCORM esportato sar\u00e0 modificabile con eXeLearning.", 
